Created attachment 30820
Patch of proposed link updates

While looking at the documentation for bug 55542, I went ahead and looked at all the links into JavaDocs and specifications. I manually opened each of them in a browser and checked that the content was right. Where I couldn't tell if there was updated information, I left it alone (so there are still a few sun.com URLs left).
Attached is a proposed patch of link updates.
